[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "黏腻、窒息，比一般的信息态空间都更为滞涩的感觉传来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "本该流动着，如潮汐般的信息正在急速下沉，彼此吸附，凝固成更为坚实的存在。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "眼瞧着危险一步步向自己逼近，胧嫣却平静地接受了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "因为痛苦、恐惧、退缩……所有所有的情感，都会稀释在磅礴海浪中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_01",
        "zh_CN": "（原来成为神就是这样一种感觉。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "因为刚才苏菲的骇入，神座系统暂时放弃了对全境机械的控制权。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但随着适格体接入，完整的神座系统，或者说“胧嫣”，开始逐渐修复、完善。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "祂的权限正在以指数级的速度变得强大。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所有的摄像头、扫描设备都化作了祂的眼睛。罗森兰的每一条街巷、每一处角落都在祂的注视之下，无所遁形。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所有机械都化作了祂的四肢、身体。在这个科技化的城市里，祂无所不能。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "专注变得不再必要，就算用千条、万条线程同时思考决策，也像是呼吸一样轻松自然。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在数十万个同时展开的感知窗口中，胧嫣看见了一切——被波及的民众、受损的建筑、一双双惊恐迷茫的眼。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "下一刻，全城的机器人又重新启动了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那些方才还在失控的钢铁之躯，此刻像是被无形的手拨正了方向。它们开始清理废墟、搬运伤员、疏导人群。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "人们错愕地盯着井然有序的机械编队，完全没注意到屏幕上的六尾狐已经悄然多了三条尾巴。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "罗森兰正在恢复它本来的模样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这一切都在安的预想之中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她早就知道，一个感受过爱的孩子，一个天然属于人类阵营的孩子，在融入神座系统的那一刻会做出怎样的选择。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "此时此刻，胧嫣终于明白了自己是为什么而存在，也明白了那些爱意从来不是没有目的的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_02",
        "zh_CN": "（妈妈她……会在睡前给我讲故事，会给我做好吃的。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "幼年胧嫣",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_20",
        "zh_CN": "妈妈，妈妈——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "安",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_ann_01",
        "zh_CN": "马上就好了——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "安",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_ann_02",
        "zh_CN": "洗手了没有？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "幼年胧嫣",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_21",
        "zh_CN": "洗干净了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "正调皮挥着带有水渍的小手时，一碗挂着红油撒着芝麻的凉粉摆在了面前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是已经忘记的味道。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就连被她用手绢擦拭嘴角的心情，也快要记不清了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "安",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_ann_03",
        "zh_CN": "慢点，慢点吃，没人跟你抢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "幼年胧嫣",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_22",
        "zh_CN": "嘶，嘶——好辣……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "安",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_ann_04",
        "zh_CN": "喝这个，来——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一碗早就晾好的竹蔗茅根水。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "凉丝丝的，甜甜的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_03",
        "zh_CN": "（她说过，对我的期望很简单……）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "安",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep4_ann_22",
        "zh_CN": "我期望……你能幸福、快乐。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "安",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep4_ann_23",
        "zh_CN": "期望你觉得来到这个世界是件幸运的事。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "安",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep4_ann_24",
        "zh_CN": "期望你能带着满心的爱意，就这么走下去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "之所以要带着满心的爱意走下去，是因为踏上这条路之后，就再也感觉不到任何爱了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "胧嫣忽然有几分庆幸，变成这样或许也是上天对她的怜悯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "因为就连痛苦也无法感知，就连无法感知痛苦的痛苦也无法感知了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可是……想对playername说的话，也永远说不出口了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在感知到自己不再是那弥散、无实体的存在，而是缓缓凝固，朝某个中心坠落之际……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "胧嫣——！胧嫣——！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_04",
        "zh_CN": "啊！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "他在呼唤着自己。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "他的声音清晰地响在耳畔。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虽然只有一瞬，但那道为自己奔来的身影还是在沉寂的海中牵动了心弦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_05",
        "zh_CN": "playername？你……为什么会来？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "循着这一丝感知，胧嫣赶紧问出了心中的疑问。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "因为下一秒，playername能带起的涟漪，也被淹没在海面上永远也不会停止的波涛中了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我不是答应过你吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_06",
        "zh_CN": "可是你答应的时候，苏菲还没对神座系统下手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_07",
        "zh_CN": "而且，妾身也说了……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_08",
        "zh_CN": "那个承诺……不用放在心上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妈妈的爱是假的，一直以来追寻的一切是假的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以这个承诺不是真的，也没有关系。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_09",
        "zh_CN": "playername，妾身送你出去吧，这里很危险。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那你呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_10",
        "zh_CN": "我？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“我”的定义是什么呢？胧嫣？还是神座系统呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她在心中问着自己。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_11",
        "zh_CN": "在彻底被“影响”前，我都会注视着罗森兰，帮助你的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep8_girl024_12",
        "zh_CN": "很可惜，如果不是苏菲从中作梗，我本有对抗埃达的力量……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这才不是你该做的事情！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你问我为什么会来，除了我们之间有约定这个理由……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还因为，那个强大、勇敢，总是仗义相助的胧嫣，值得我为她而来！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "抓住我！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "像海中漂泊的人终于找到了一块浮木，宽厚手掌牢牢抓住了自己的手臂。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那个身影就这样出现在眼前——没有迟疑，没有犹豫，实实在在地履行着自己的承诺。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好像对他而言，这不过是世上最理所当然的事。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "炽烈的真心照亮了整个晦暗的空间，所有纷杂的信息都在这道光辉下变得模糊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 71,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不自觉地，她伸手触摸着那道光。曾经的自己也好像做过一样的动作。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 72,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc36ep1_girl024_53",
        "zh_CN": "世上……真有这样的人吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 73,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "胧嫣瑞狐",
